Sorry it's taking me so long.  I got Jesse v.02 ready; for right now,
I'd recommend the downloading the Gladiator Scenario Convertor by
Deathifier if all you're looking for is info on the scenario file.

* * *

I've been updating my antivirus program because a couple of trojan
virii got into on my system and I cleaned it out yesterday.  The virus
scanners have constistently said that Jsse was clean. :-)

I'm figuring out which files needed to be included with Jesse when I
compile it next time as well starting to write some documentation.

Overall, I'm happy with the thumbnail maps I'm getting.
